==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Feeding
<hw>Feed"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the act of eating, or
of supplying with food; the process of fattening.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is eaten; food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>That which furnishes or affords food, especially for
animals; pasture land.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Feeding bottle</b></col>. <cd>See under
<er>Bottle</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fee-faw-fum</ent>⟦br⟧
